flowchart LR
    U[Users: SRE | Platform | CMDB Admin | Leadership]
    FE[Experience Layer\nSearch + 3D Graph + Panels + Filters]
    API[API Delivery Layer\nGraph | CI | Search | Health | ETL Status]
    ORCH[Backend Orchestration\nValidation | Timing | Rate Control | Policy]
    GRAPH[Graph Store\nCI Nodes + Directed Relationships]
    CACHE[Cache Store\nNeighborhood + CI Detail + Search Results]
    SEARCH[Search Index\nFast Retrieval + Facets]
    ETL[ETL Pipeline\nFull Sync + Incremental Sync + Validation]
    SNOW[ServiceNow CMDB\nCI + Relationship Source]
    OBS[Observability\nLatency + Throughput + Health]
    SEC[Security & Governance\nSecrets + Input Safety + Access Control]
    DEVOPS[Local-First Operations\nCompose + Healthchecks + Volumes]

    U --> FE
    FE --> API
    API --> ORCH
    ORCH --> GRAPH
    ORCH --> CACHE
    ORCH --> SEARCH
    ETL --> GRAPH
    ETL --> SEARCH
    SNOW --> ETL
    ORCH --> OBS
    ETL --> OBS
    API --> SEC
    ORCH --> SEC
    API --> DEVOPS
    ETL --> DEVOPS